Class City

  • java.lang.Object
    • sajas.core.Agent
      • agents.City
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    sajas.core.TimerListener

    public class City
extends sajas.core.Agent
    Agent that represents the city structure and displays in the space the image correspondent to the map. It's responsible of creating the semaphore managers regarding the intersections in the city structure.
